{"type":null,"faqId":19327,"title":"手机屏幕亮度/色彩异常","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.s3{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005702991\"></a><span>请确认光感应器是否正常。光感应器被异物遮挡可能引起屏幕亮度异常。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>如果感觉屏幕偏亮或偏暗，请调整屏幕亮度。下拉状态栏，点击 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64221\" style=\"width:0.22986111in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，滑动屏幕亮度图标右侧的滑块设置亮度。也可以在</span><span class=\"s2\">设置</span><span>中的</span><span class=\"s2\">全部设置</span><span>页签下，点击</span><span class=\"s2\">显示</span><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s2\">亮度</span><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1<a name=\"_Toc408418071\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64222\" style=\"width:5.0in;height:2.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以实际手机界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>对于 </span><span class=\"s3\">EMUI 2.3</span><span> 及以上系统，请确认是否进入</span><span class=\"s2\">超级省电</span><span>模式。超级省电模式下，屏幕会变暗，且只能使用电话、信息和联系人功能。点击</span><span class=\"s2\">退出</span><span>即可退出超级省电模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-2<a name=\"_Toc408418072\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64223\" style=\"width:5.0in;height:2.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以实际手机界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>如果屏幕曾受到外部冲击，内部液晶可能会破损并导致屏幕亮度或色彩异常。请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2468","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608222000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":29,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}